      <chapter>
        <title>Global Annual Growth Rate Projections to 2024</title>
        <paragraph>The researchers at the Center for International Development at Harvard University use their newly updated measure of economic complexity, which captures the diversity and sophistication of productive capabilities embedded in a country’s exports, to generate the global growth projections.</paragraph>
        <paragraph>The World Bank estimates that India’s economy is currently growing at a fast pace and forecasts it is likely to remain the world’s fastest growing large economy for the foreseeable future.</paragraph>
